OL,3,CTourette's campaigner apologises to
OL,4,CSinners actors after BAFTA racial slur
OL,6,FTourette's campaigner John Davidson
OL,7,Fhas issued an apology to Michael B.
OL,8,FJordan and Delroy Lindo after his
OL,9,Fcondition caused him to shout a racial
OL,10,Fslur at the actors during the BAFTA
OL,11,FFilm Awards, his team has said.
OL,13,FIn his first interview since the
OL,14,Fincident, Davidson described feeling a
OL,15,F"wave of shame" when he shouted the
OL,16,Foffensive term at the Sinners actors
OL,17,Fas they presented an award on February
OL,18,F22.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
