PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772107375
OL,3,CTourette's campaigner apologises to
OL,4,CSinners actors after BAFTA racial slur
OL,6,FThe 54-year-old has a particular type
OL,7,Fof Tourette's called coprolalia, which
OL,8,Fincludes involuntary outbursts of
OL,9,Fobscene words or socially
OL,10,Finappropriate remarks, according to
OL,11,Fthe Tourette Association of America.
OL,13,FThe BBC has been heavily criticised
OL,14,Ffor not editing out the slur from the
OL,15,Fbroadcast, and on Wednesday, the BBC
OL,16,Fsaid there had been a "serious
OL,17,Fmistake."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
