FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772107375
OL,3,CTourette's campaigner apologises to
OL,4,CSinners actors after BAFTA racial slur
OL,6,FThe organisation's Director General
OL,7,Fasked the Executive Complaints Unit to
OL,8,Fcomplete a fast-tracked investigation
OL,9,Fand provide a full response to
OL,10,Fcomplainants."
OL,12,FDavidson said his tics had started as
OL,13,Fnoises and movements as he sat in the
OL,14,Faudience at the Royal Festival Hall,
OL,15,Fbut "ramped up" as he grew more
OL,16,Fnervous.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
