PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772107375
OL,3,CTourette's campaigner apologises to
OL,4,CSinners actors after BAFTA racial slur
OL,6,F"When my coprolalia tics came out, my
OL,7,Fstomach just dropped. As always, I
OL,8,Ffelt a wave of shame and embarrassment
OL,9,Fhit me all at once," Davidson told
OL,10,FVariety in an email interview.
OL,12,F"You want the floor to swallow you up.
OL,13,FI wanted to disappear. I wanted to
OL,14,Fhide - just get away from all the
OL,15,Feyes."
OL,17,FDavidson was attending the ceremony
OL,18,Fafter inspiring the film, I Swear,
OL,19,Fwhich dramatises his life with severe
OL,20,FTourette syndrome.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
