PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772107375
OL,3,CTourette's campaigner apologises to
OL,4,CSinners actors after BAFTA racial slur
OL,6,FAfter noticing his tics could be heard
OL,7,Ffrom the stage, he said he left his
OL,8,Fseat and watched the rest of the
OL,9,Fceremony on a monitor in a private
OL,10,Froom.
OL,12,FDavidson said that comments presuming
OL,13,Fhe had control over his tics or is
OL,14,F"racist deep down" have been deeply
OL,15,Fupsetting for him, and proved there
OL,16,Fwas still much to do in combating
OL,17,Fstigma surrounding Tourette syndrome.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
