PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772107375
OL,3,CTourette's campaigner apologises to
OL,4,CSinners actors after BAFTA racial slur
OL,6,F"The awards were, in all honesty, just
OL,7,Fa heightened version of my everyday
OL,8,Flife and are the reason why, for many
OL,9,Fperiods in my life, I have been
OL,10,Ffearful of leaving the house - because
OL,11,FI am so anxious and nervous about what
OL,12,FI might tic and what people's reaction
OL,13,Fmight be," the campaigner said.
OL,15,FDavidson's team said he had apologised
OL,16,Fto Jordan, Lindo ,and production
OL,17,Fdesigner Hannah Beachler via Warner
OL,18,FBros, the studio behind Sinners, which
OL,19,Fwon three awards during the evening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
