PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772107375
OL,3,CTourette's campaigner apologises to
OL,4,CSinners actors after BAFTA racial slur
OL,6,FNeither Jordan nor Lindo have issued a
OL,7,Fstatement about the incident.
OL,9,FBeachler said she had also been on the
OL,10,Freceiving end of a racial slur at
OL,11,Fanother point of the evening, and
OL,12,Fcriticised the on-stage apology issued
OL,13,Fby host Alan Cumming during the awards.
OL,15,FCumming had made reference to "some
OL,16,Fstrong and offensive language" heard
OL,17,Fin the audience and said: "We
OL,18,Fapologise if you were offended".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772107375
OL,3,CTourette's campaigner apologises to
OL,4,CSinners actors after BAFTA racial slur
OL,6,FBeachler wrote on X: "I understand and
OL,7,Fdeeply know why this is an impossible
OL,8,Fsituation. I know we must handle this
OL,9,Fwith grace and continue to push
OL,10,Fthrough. But what made the situation
OL,11,Fworse was the throw away apology of
OL,12,F'if you were offended' at the end of
OL,13,Fthe show."
OL,15,F"Of course we were offended...but our
OL,16,Ffrequency, our spiritual vibration is
OL,17,Ftuned to a higher level than what
OL,18,Fhappened. I am not steal (sic), this
OL,19,Fdid not bounce off of me, but I exist
OL,20,Fabove it."
