OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772107375
OL,3,CTourette's campaigner apologises to
OL,4,CSinners actors after BAFTA racial slur
OL,6,FActor Jamie Foxx also called the
OL,7,Fincident "unacceptable", claiming that
OL,8,FDavidson had meant what he said in a
OL,9,Fseries of comments on Instagram.
OL,11,FThe BBC already apologised for not
OL,12,Fediting out the slur shouted during
OL,13,Fthe ceremony, which was broadcast on
OL,14,FSunday night, with producers
OL,15,Foverseeing the coverage stating that
OL,16,Fthey did not hear it.
OL,18,FA spokesperson said: "Some viewers may
OL,19,Fhave heard strong and offensive
OL,20,Flanguage during the BAFTA Film Awards
OL,21,F2026.
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@WO]zD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
