PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772107375
OL,3,CTourette's campaigner apologises to
OL,4,CSinners actors after BAFTA racial slur
OL,6,F"This arose from involuntary verbal
OL,7,Ftics associated with Tourette
OL,8,Fsyndrome, and was not intentional. We
OL,9,Fapologise for any offence caused by
OL,10,Fthe language heard.
OL,12,F"We apologise that this was not edited
OL,13,Fout prior to broadcast, and it will
OL,14,Fnow be removed from the version on BBC
OL,15,FiPlayer."
OL,17,FBAFTA also issued a statement on
OL,18,FMonday apologising to Jordan and
OL,19,FLindo, and thanking them for their
OL,20,F"incredible dignity and
OL,21,Fprofessionalism".
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
