PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772107375
OL,3,CTourette's campaigner apologises to
OL,4,CSinners actors after BAFTA racial slur
OL,6,FIt also told members that a
OL,7,Fcomprehensive review into what
OL,8,Fhappened is underway, in a letter seen
OL,9,Fby ITV News.
OL,11,F"We take full responsibility for
OL,12,Fputting our guests in a very difficult
OL,13,Fsituation and we apologise to all,"
OL,14,FBAFTA said in a statement.
OL,16,F"We will learn from this, and keep
OL,17,Finclusion at the core of all we do,
OL,18,Fmaintaining our belief in film and
OL,19,Fstorytelling as a critical conduit for
OL,20,Fcompassion and empathy."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
