PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772107375
OL,3,CTourette's campaigner apologises to
OL,4,CSinners actors after BAFTA racial slur
OL,6,FDavidson was made an MBE in 2019 for
OL,7,Fhis efforts to increase understanding
OL,8,Fof Tourette syndrome and help families
OL,9,Fdeal with the condition. I Swear tells
OL,10,Fthe story of his life with the
OL,11,Fcondition, which he developed at age
OL,12,F12.
OL,14,FThe actor Robert Aramayo, who played
OL,15,FDavidson in the film, scooped the
OL,16,Faward for best actor on the night.
OL,18,FIn a statement, UK charity Tourettes
OL,19,FAction called the backlash towards
OL,20,FDavidson "extremely saddening" and
OL,21,Fasked people to watch I Swear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
