OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772107375
OL,3,CTourette's campaigner apologises to
OL,4,CSinners actors after BAFTA racial slur
OL,6,F"People with Tourette's can say words
OL,7,For phrases they do not mean, do not
OL,8,Fendorse, and feel great distress about
OL,9,Fafterwards," the charity said.
OL,11,F"These symptoms are neurological, not
OL,12,Fintentional, and they are something
OL,13,FJohn - like many others with
OL,14,FTourette's - lives with every single
OL,15,Fday."
OL,17,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,18,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,19,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,20,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
